s="step 5">Once you have reached the <strong>My Rewards</strong> page, press the indicated key to switch to the <strong>SHiFT Code</strong> page.</div><div class="step 6">Enter the 25-character SHiFT Code into the provided fields. Once you are finished, click <em>Submit</em>.</div><div class="step 7">If successful, you will receive a confirmation message. The reward from the SHiFT Code will also appear on the <strong>My Rewards</strong> page.</div><div class="step 8">You can now make your way to the <strong>Golden Chest</strong> in <strong>Sanctuary</strong> to spend your Golden Keys. The Golden Chest is located in the same room as the <strong>Fast Travel Station</strong>. Opening the chest will cost <strong>one Golden Key</strong>, and the rewards will be droppped at the <strong>level of your current character</strong>, regardless of playthrough.</div></div><?php include_once('local/support-footer.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/afterContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/sharedScripts.php'); ?><script async src="/assets/scripts/min/local/help/how-to-redeem/instructions.min.js?v=<?php echo $svQueryString; ?>"></script>